data.description: REDUCED UNDER $400,000!!! BRING ALL OFFERS! STUNNING ONE OWNER HOME IN THE WEATHERBY!  MOTIVATED SELLER!  4 bedroom, 3 and 1/2 baths on approximately 1/2 acre lot.  Custom bonus room upstairs complete with bath and walk in closet is the 4th bedroom. Upstairs bath has a large custom all natural stone tile shower with bench, rainmaker showerhead, and seamless rubbed oil bronze and glass shower doors. Living room has dual sided gas fireplace between great room and sunroom. Kitchen with granite countertops, pantry and custom cabinets. There's a breakfast area with a separate formal dining room. Split floor plan with 2 bedrooms on one side of house connected to a Jack and Jill full bath as well as an office area.  A spacious primary suite has dual vanities, jetted tub and separate shower. Upgraded real oak hardwood flooring in main living areas and kitchen; carpet in bedrooms and tile in bathrooms. Lots of upgrades including double tray ceilings, wainscoting, judges paneling, crown molding in every room and custom wood blinds throughout. Privacy fenced back yard with patio and full sprinkler system. Both HVAC units replaced 2018 and still under warranty. County taxes only. Conveniently located near shopping, schools, medical facilities, a movie theatre, I-75 and RAFB.  Call me today for your private showing appointment.
